#Text=1 . An antimicrobial material comprising : at least one yarn comprising fine fiber of 1.0 denier or less ; and at least one yarn comprising antimicrobial fiber engaged with said yarn comprising fine fiber .
#Text=2 . The material of claim 1 , wherein said material is woven .
#Text=3 . The material of claim 1 , wherein said material is knitted .
#Text=4 . The material of claim 1 , wherein said fine fiber is capable of removing microbes from a surface .

#Text=5 . The material of claim 1 , wherein said antimicrobial fiber comprises an acetate fiber spun together with a synthetic fiber , said antimicrobial fiber imparting an antimicrobial property to the entire material .
#Text=6 . The material of claim 5 , wherein said synthetic fiber is polyester .
#Text=7 . The material of claim 1 , wherein said fine fiber is less than 4 microns diameter .
#Text=8 . The material of claim 1 , wherein said fine fiber comprises polyamide and imparts an overall catiomc charge to said material .
#Text=9 The material of claim 1 , wherein said fine fiber is 0.5 denier or less .
#Text=10 . The material of claim 1 , wherein said fine fiber is 0.3 denier or less .

#Text=11 . A cleaning cloth comprising : at least one yarn comprising fine fiber of 1.0 denier or less ; at least one yarn comprising antimicrobial fiber engaged with said yarn of fine fiber , said antimicrobial fiber comprising an acetate fiber spun together with a synthetic fiber , wherein said antimicrobial fiber imparts an antimicrobial property to the entire cloth and said fine fibers are capable of removing microbes from a surface .
#Text=12 The cleaning cloth of claim 11 , wherein said cleaning cloth is woven .
#Text=13 . The cleaning cloth of claim 12 , wherein said cleaning cloth is knitted .
#Text=14 . The cleaning cloth of claim 11 , wherein said synthetic fiber is polyester .
#Text=15 . The cleaning cloth of claim 11 , wherein said fine fiber is 0.5 denier or less .
#Text=16 . The cleaning cloth of claim 11 , wherein said fine fiber is 0.3 denier or less .
#Text=17 . The cleaning cloth of claim 16 , wherein said fine fiber has a diameter of less than 4 microns .
#Text=18 . The cleaning cloth of claim 11 , wherein said fine fiber comprises polyamide and impart a cationic charge to said cleaning cloth .

#Text=19 An antimicrobial cleaning cloth comprising : at least one yarn comprising fine fiber of 0.3 denier or less ; at least one yarn comprising antimicrobial fiber engaged with said yarn comprising fine fiber ; wherein said fine fiber is capable of removing microbes from a surface , and said antimicrobial fibers impart an antimicrobial property to the entire cloth .
#Text=20 . The cleaning cloth of claim 19 , wherein said cleaning cloth is woven .
#Text=21 . The cleaning cloth according to claim 19 , wherein said cleaning cloth is knitted .
#Text=22 . The cleaning cloth of claim 19 , wherein said antimicrobial fiber comprises an acetate fiber spun together with polyester .
#Text=23 . The cleaning cloth of claim 19 , wherein said fine fiber is less than 4 microns m diameter .
#Text=24 . The cleaning cloth of claim 19 , wherein said fine fiber comprises polyamide and imparts a cationic charge to the entire cloth .
#Text=25 . The cleaning cloth of claim 19 , wherein said antimicrobial fiber further comprises the antimicrobial agent triclosan .
#Text=26 . An antimicrobial material comprising : at least one yarn comprising antimicrobial fiber and fine fiber of less than 1.0 denier .
#Text=27 . The material of claim 26 , wherein said material is woven .
#Text=28 . The material of claim 26 , wherein said material is knitted .
